          "question": "<p><a name=\"8039\"></a><div itemprop=\"text\"><p>In a triangle \\( PQR, PS \\) is the angle bisector of \\( \\angle QPR \\text{ and } \\angle QPS =60^\\circ \\). What is the length of \\( PS \\) ?</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"images/gateOverflow_pyq_images/general_aptitude___quantitative_aptitude___triangles/80087f128e66ec1ee93ad8dc489c3107.png\"></p>\n\n</div><br><br><b>GATE CSE 2015 Set 2 | Question: GA-8</b></p>",
